  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Assessments (survey data) in this study are designed to sample the symptom burden of patients
      undergoing adjuvant and neoadjuvant chemotherapy in the hospital. There will be no change in
      the treatment plan for these patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
